        "TileImage": "$($repository cafb2bda-485c-4c11-9df0-c1e6971dbbbb).Image",
        "Description": "The IOI Decorations Supplier hasn&apos;t been updating their new year lanterns since the year of rat, so 47 was planning to buy himself a Fort Mustang as the gift of the year of horse.\r\rHowever, he found out none of the local car delearships sells them, only Louis Bubblebee avaliable. Now 47 is angry like a 4.7-year-old who wants his candy.\r\rHelp him blow up all three Bubblebee sports cars along with their drivers, consider it the new year fireworks.\r\rHappy New Year 47.",
